[ZMapp has evidently become available again, but just like so many other Africans in Sierra Leone, he started his treatment too late in the course of the disease. - Mod.JW]

******
[2] USA: cost of treatment
Date: Tue 18 Nov 2014
Source: NBC News [edited]
http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/ebola-virus-outbreak/cost-treat-ebola-1-million-two-patients-n250986


It cost more than USD one million to treat 2 patients sent to the Nebraska Medical Center, a hospital official testified on Tues [18 Nov 2014], and it's still not clear who will pay the bill and how. It's the 1st on-the-record estimate of what it has cost to treat Ebola patients in the United States.

So far, 10 people have been treated on U.S. soil; most recently, [a doctor] who died Mon 17 Nov 2014]... - more

