******
[3] UK: Royal family speaks out on Ebola & malaria
Date: 19 Nov 2014
Source: Daily Mail [edited]
http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2840343/Queen-warns-against-focusing-ebola-Majesty-says-worries-disease-overshadow-deadlier-conditions-including-malaria.html


The Queen has asked "piercing" questions about how the disease ought to be controlled. She is worried that Ebola is overshadowing risks from diseases like malaria.

Ebola has claimed 5000 lives. Malaria kills the same number every week.

[Byline: Francesca Infante]

